#: of numpy.polynomial.laguerre.lagfromroots:31
msgid ""
"1-D array of coefficients.  If all roots are real then `out` is a real "
"array, if some of the roots are complex, then `out` is complex even if all "
"the coefficients in the result are real (see Examples below)."
msgstr ""

